
!!!
%html
  %head
    %title Wistia Learning Center
    %link{ :rel => 'stylesheet', :href => 'stylesheets/project.css' }

  %body
    #global-header-container.cf
      #global-header.cf
        .logo
          %a{ :href => 'http://www.wistia.com' }
        .links
          %a{ :href => '#' } Learning
          %a{ :href => '#' } Pricing
          %a{ :href => '#' } Blog
          %a{ :href => '#' } Login

    #local-header-container
      #local-header.cf
        .light-bulb
          %img{ :src => 'images/lightbulb.png' }
        .project-title
          %h1 Video Production
        .project-description
          Description of this project and what it's about, as well as permalinks to a related blog post and, if it exists, a link to download whatever other materials we've produced for this topic that doesn't fit into a video, proper.

    #media-tiles-container
      #media-tiles.cf
        - 5.times do
          .media-tile-container
            .media-tile
              %img{ :src => 'images/large_play_button.png' }
              .title Media title
              .description A brief description of what the video is about - something punchy and short!
              
